'''Rolf-Dieter Jaretzky''' (born 1935) is a pharmacist and philatelist who signed the [[Roll of Distinguished Philatelists]] in 1997.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aiep-experts.net/experts/experts/userprofile/JARETZKYRDP.html|title=JARETZKY, RDP|website=www.aiep-experts.net}}</ref>
He was the president of the Grand Prix Club (1994-1996) and the director of the Bundesstelle Ausstellungswesen des BDPh. He is a fellow of the [[Royal Philatelic Society of London]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aephil.com/en/membersfiche.asp?id=62|title=Académie Européenne de Philatélie|website=www.aephil.com}}</ref>
He has formed leading collections of the philately of Mexico<ref>{{cite web|url=https://corinphila.ch/en/_ptshop/?action=show_item&id=2#|title=Vol. 2: Mexico • The Rolf Dieter Jaretzky Collection - Corinphila Auctions - Stamps|website=Corinphila Auktionen}}</ref> and Prussia.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.heinrich-koehler.de/en/vol-43-prussia-%E2%80%A2-rolf-dieter-jaretzky-collection|title=Vol. 43: Prussia - The Rolf Dieter Jaretzky Collection - Germany's oldest stamp auction house - Heinrich Koehler - Stamp Auction House|website=www.heinrich-koehler.de}}</ref>
